7 STATED IN 18 U.S.C. 2339A.
8 (4) “NONPROFIT ORGANIZATION” MEANS A BUSINESS ENTITY THAT:
9 (I) IS EXEMPT FROM FEDERAL INCOME TAXES UNDER § 501 OF
10 THE INTERNAL REVENUE CODE; AND
11 (II) HAS BEEN GRANTED:
12 1. AN INCOME TAX EXEMPTION UNDER § 10–104 OF THIS
